    "Title": "晚归",
    "Content": "晚上8点，美中关系全国委员组织的美国国会代表团的来访。大约14个人在锦江饭店附近一直聊到11点，刚刚回来，有些累。<br/><br/>之后，老朋友白莉娟女士（<a href=\"http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&newwindow=1&rlz=1B2GGGL_zh-CNCN209CN209&q=jan+berris&btnG=Search\">Jan Berris</a>）送了我本书，名叫：<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Collapse-Societies-Choose-Fail-Succeed/dp/0670033375\">Collapse, How Societies Choose to Fail or Succeed</a>。扉页上用花体英文写着：<br/><blockquote>July 6, 2007<br/>To Wang Jian Shuo,<br/>Who is always so helpful and who has so many interesting things to share.<br/>US-China Working Group,<br/>National Committee on US-China Relations.</blockquote>这是我第三次和Jan一起来接待来自美国政府的官员，上一次是市长代表团，就在上个月，还有一次是去年六月，是美国知识分子代表团。。。",
