    "id": 1025,
    "Title": "怎么没想到呢？",
    "Content": "1993年，Marc Andreessen写了一封很重要的<a href=\"http://1997.webhistory.org/www.lists/www-talk.1993q1/0182.html\">邮件</a>：<br/><blockquote>I'd like to propose a new, optional HTML tag:<br/><br/>&nbsp;<br/><br/>IMG<br/><br/>&nbsp;<br/><br/>Required argument is SRC=\"url\".<br/><br/>&nbsp;<br/><br/>This names a bitmap or pixmap file for the browser to attempt to pull<br/>over the network and interpret as an image, to be embedded in the text<br/>at the point of the tag's occurrence.<br/><br/>An example is:<br/><br/>&lt;IMG SRC=\"<a href=\"file://foobar.com/foo/bar/blargh.xbm\">file://foobar.com/foo/bar/blargh.xbm</a>\"&gt;<br/><br/>&nbsp;</blockquote><br/>现在看起来多正常呀，但是这个IMG标签成就了Netscape的成功，也成就了现代的互联网。",
