    "Content": "我把上一篇文章《<a href=\"http://home.wangjianshuo.com/cn/?p=1110\">人们跟随他们相信的</a>》提及的几个广告片放在这里。（当然在YouTube上面，我相信你有自己的访问真正的世界的办法）。<br/><br/><strong>Miss Mary</strong><br/><br/><a href=\"http://home.wangjianshuo.com/cn/2013/06/missmarycoke.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1112\" alt=\"missmarycoke\" src=\"http://home.wangjianshuo.com/cn/2013/06/missmarycoke-300x166.jpeg\" width=\"300\" height=\"166\" /></a><br/><br/><b>板凳</b><br/><br/>（还没有找到）<br/><br/><strong>I’d Like to Buy the World a Coke</strong><br/><br/><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/1VM2eLhvsSM\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><br/><br/><strong>固执的乐观</strong><br/><br/><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/mS0-r1JFNBY?rel=0\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><br/><br/><strong>我爱你非洲</strong><br/><br/><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/rb6yctYKfhs\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><br/><br/><strong>监控录像</strong><br/><br/><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ceTBF1Hik5I?rel=0\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><br/><br/><strong>小世界机器</strong><br/><br/><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ts_4vOUDImE?rel=0\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>",
